{"title": "PC March 23 - India - March 23 Antimperialist day in memory of revolutionary martyrs", "published time": "2024-03-23T17:18:00+08:00", "images": ["https://www.redspark.nu/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/1380275411-1051-800x445.jpg"], "content": "<div class=\"post-body entry-content\" id=\"post-body-2860521329002285896\" itemprop=\"description articleBody\"><p></p><p align=\"center\" class=\"western\" style=\"line-height: 100%; margin-bottom: 0cm; margin-left: 2.6cm; orphans: 2; widows: 2;\"><br/></p><p align=\"center\" class=\"western\" style=\"line-height: 100%; margin-bottom: 0cm; margin-left: 2.3cm; orphans: 2; widows: 2;\"><span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, serif;\"><span><span lang=\"it-IT\"><b>PARTY\nCOMMUNIST OF INDIA (MAOIST)</b></span></span></span></span></p><p align=\"center\" class=\"western\" style=\"line-height: 100%; margin-bottom: 0cm; margin-left: 2.6cm; orphans: 2; widows: 2;\"><span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, serif;\"><span lang=\"it-IT\">Office \n Central regional</span></span></span></p><p align=\"center\" class=\"western\" style=\"line-height: 100%; margin-bottom: 0cm; margin-left: 2.6cm; orphans: 2; widows: 2;\"><br/></p><p align=\"center\" class=\"western\" style=\"line-height: 100%; margin-bottom: 0cm; margin-left: 2.6cm; orphans: 2; widows: 2;\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"attachment-colormag-featured-image size-colormag-featured-image wp-post-image\" height=\"223\" src=\"../Images/2024-03-23T17-18-00-08-00/000000.jpg\" srcset=\"../Images/2024-03-23T17-18-00-08-00/000000.jpg\" width=\"400\"/></p><p align=\"right\" class=\"western\" style=\"line-height: 100%; margin-bottom: 0cm;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, serif;\"><span><span lang=\"it-IT\"><b>20 \n Marzo 2022</b></span></span></span></p><p align=\"right\" class=\"western\" style=\"line-height: 100%; margin-bottom: 0cm;\"><br/></p><p align=\"center\" class=\"western\" style=\"line-height: 100%; margin-bottom: 0cm;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, serif;\"><span lang=\"it-IT\"><b>We celebrate the historian \n March 23 as an antimperialist day,<br/>in the immortal memory \n Of the revolutionary companions Bhagat Singh, Sukdev and Rajguru!<br/></b></span></span><br/></p><p align=\"center\" class=\"western\" style=\"line-height: 100%; margin-bottom: 0cm;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, serif;\"><span lang=\"it-IT\"><b>We defeat \n imperialism,</b></span></span><span style=\"font-variant: normal;\"><span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, serif;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: normal;\"><span lang=\"it-IT\"><b>d</b></span></span></span></span></span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, serif;\"><span lang=\"it-IT\"><b>we instruct \n Brahmanic Fascism Hindutva!</b></span></span></p><p align=\"center\" class=\"western\" style=\"line-height: 100%; margin-bottom: 0cm;\"><br/></p><p align=\"center\" class=\"western\" style=\"line-height: 100%; margin-bottom: 0cm;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, serif;\"><span lang=\"it-IT\"><b>We continue ours \n Fight to realize the dreams of all the great martyrs of the movement \n For freedom and we fight for India of new democracy</b></span></span></p><p align=\"left\" class=\"western\" style=\"line-height: 100%; margin-bottom: 0cm;\"><br/></p><p align=\"justify\" class=\"western\" style=\"line-height: 100%; margin-bottom: 0cm; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0.5cm; widows: 2;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, serif;\"><span><span lang=\"it-IT\">In the \n long history of struggle of our popular democratic movement, the \n March 23 has a particular revolutionary value in everyone's heart \n how many are fighting for a right and at the same time company \n they resolutely despise imperialism. On 23 March the companions \n Bhagat Singh, SukDev and Rajguru have been hanged by power \n British colonial to crush the liberation movement \n anti-colonial of that time. The victory of the Bolshevik Revolution \n he had influenced these three Indian revolutionaries who formed \n of HSRA (Hindustan's socialist revolutionary association). The \n Comrade Baghat Singh played a fundamental role in training \n of the HSRA, and clearly stated that whatever the color \n dominant classes, whether they are white, black or other skin, it must be \n continue the fight against all exploiters.</span></span></span></p><p align=\"justify\" class=\"western\" style=\"line-height: 100%; margin-bottom: 0cm; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0.5cm; widows: 2;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, serif;\"><span><span lang=\"it-IT\">Those \n same exploiters colluded with the imperialists</span></span></span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, serif;\"><span><span lang=\"it-IT\"><span style=\"font-weight: normal;\">Today</span></span></span></span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, serif;\"><span><span lang=\"it-IT\">celebrate \n their martyrdom and in particular the management of the Arss celebrates it \n who opposed it hard to Bhagat Singh and his cause. The BJP, \n Political organ of the Arss, today claims all the fighters for the \n freedom, including the companions Bhagat Singh and his own, have no one \n moral law even to talk about fighters for freedom e \n to distort their movement. Our party, PCI (Maoist), \n makes them their homage revolutionary and fights for the \n realization of their revolutionary aspirations.</span></span></span></p><p align=\"justify\" class=\"western\" style=\"line-height: 100%; margin-bottom: 0cm; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0.5cm; widows: 2;\"><br/></p><p align=\"justify\" class=\"western\" style=\"line-height: 100%; margin-bottom: 0cm; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0.5cm; widows: 2;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, serif;\"><span><span lang=\"it-IT\"/span></span></span></p><p align=\"justify\" class=\"western\" style=\"line-height: 100%; margin-bottom: 0cm; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0.5cm; widows: 2;\"><br/></p><p align=\"justify\" class=\"western\" style=\"line-height: 100%; margin-bottom: 0cm; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0.5cm; widows: 2;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, serif;\"><span><span lang=\"it-IT\"/span></span></span></p><p align=\"justify\" class=\"western\" style=\"line-height: 100%; margin-bottom: 0cm; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0.5cm; widows: 2;\"><br/></p><p align=\"justify\" class=\"western\" style=\"line-height: 100%; margin-bottom: 0cm; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0.5cm; widows: 2;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, serif;\"><span><span lang=\"it-IT\"/span></span></span></p><p align=\"justify\" class=\"western\" style=\"line-height: 100%; margin-bottom: 0cm; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0.5cm; widows: 2;\"><br/></p><p align=\"justify\" class=\"western\" style=\"line-height: 100%; margin-bottom: 0cm; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0.5cm; widows: 2;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, serif;\"><span><span lang=\"it-IT\">The \n Central Committee of the PCI (Maoist) appeals to all democrats, \n patriots, workers, peasants, dalits and women's organizations, \n of the Adivasi, of students, writers, teachers, lawyers and \n Human rights activists to celebrate March 23 with spirit \n Antimperialist and revolutionary enthusiasm. Appeals to keep \n seminars, meetings, events supporting the ideas of \n Comrades Bhagat Singh, Sukdev and Rajguru to report the subtle \n attempts of the Hindutva forces to saffron Bhagat Singh and i \n his companions.</span></span></span></p><p align=\"justify\" class=\"western\" style=\"line-height: 100%; margin-bottom: 0cm; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0.5cm; widows: 2;\"><br/></p><p align=\"justify\" class=\"western\" style=\"line-height: 100%; margin-bottom: 0cm; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0.5cm; widows: 2;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, serif;\"><span><span lang=\"it-IT\"><b>Death \n to imperialism!</b></span></span></span></p><p align=\"justify\" class=\"western\" style=\"line-height: 100%; margin-bottom: 0cm; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0.5cm; widows: 2;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, serif;\"><span><span lang=\"it-IT\"><b>Death \n To the fascism Brahmanico Hindutva!</b></span></span></span></p><p align=\"justify\" class=\"western\" style=\"line-height: 100%; margin-bottom: 0cm; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0.5cm; widows: 2;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, serif;\"><span><span lang=\"it-IT\"><b>Alive \n Il Marxismo-Leninism-Maoism!</b></span></span></span></p><p align=\"justify\" class=\"western\" style=\"line-height: 100%; margin-bottom: 0cm; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0.5cm; widows: 2;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, serif;\"><span><span lang=\"it-IT\"><b>Viva \n Bhagat Singh of E -Copg, Sukhdev A Rajguru!</b></span></span></span></p><p align=\"justify\" class=\"western\" style=\"line-height: 100%; margin-bottom: 0cm; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0.5cm; widows: 2;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, serif;\"><span><span lang=\"it-IT\"><b>Inquilab \n Zindabad!</b></span></span></span></p><p align=\"justify\" class=\"western\" style=\"line-height: 100%; margin-bottom: 0cm; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0.5cm; widows: 2;\"><br/></p><p align=\"right\" class=\"western\" style=\"line-height: 100%; margin-bottom: 0cm;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, serif;\"><span><span lang=\"it-IT\"><b>Greetings \n revolutionaries</b></span></span></span></p><p align=\"right\" class=\"western\" style=\"line-height: 100%; margin-bottom: 0cm;\"><br/></p><p align=\"right\" class=\"western\" style=\"line-height: 100%; margin-bottom: 0cm;\"><br/></p><p align=\"right\" class=\"western\" style=\"line-height: 100%; margin-bottom: 0cm;\"><br/></p><p align=\"right\" class=\"western\" style=\"line-height: 100%; margin-bottom: 0cm;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, serif;\"><span><span lang=\"it-IT\"><b>Pratap</b></span></span></span></p><p align=\"right\" class=\"western\" style=\"line-height: 100%; margin-bottom: 0cm;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, serif;\"><span><span lang=\"it-IT\"><b>Spokesman</b></span></span></span></p><p align=\"right\" class=\"western\" style=\"line-height: 100%; margin-bottom: 0cm;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, serif;\"><span><span lang=\"it-IT\"><b>Office \n Central 